thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Sandy

author: Sandy
title: Sandy
text:
We have found this company to be" one out of the box" (excuse the pun)
All staff have been friendly, professional, helpful and obliging.
They all have a happy disposition which makes interacting with them a pleasure.
I really didn't expect this experience , but am so pleased we decided to use Taxibox.
